      <title>联发科天玑 9500 登场：4.21Ghz 超大核、双 NPU、vivo X300 首发</title>
      <description>&lt;figure class="mb-module-gap"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto w-fit"&gt;&lt;img alt="联发科天玑 9500 登场：4.21Ghz 超大核、双 NPU、vivo X300 首发" class="rounded-lg" loading="lazy" height="505" src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rzpqT_N5Iy6azEtY9cv0XA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-09/28abdc60-978d-11f0-9efc-ba374943c9f0" width="960" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;figcaption class="text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere" style="max-width:960px"&gt;联发科天玑 9500 登场：4.21Ghz 超大核、双 NPU、vivo X300 首发&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;联发科技今日正式带来新一代旗舰手机 SoC &lt;a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.mediatek.tw/products/smartphones-2/mediatek-dimensity-9500" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:天玑 9500;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;天玑 9500&lt;/a&gt;。它基于台积电第三代 3nm 制程，CPU 和 GPU 效能分别较前代提升了 17% 和 33%。其中 CPU 为全大核架构，采用 1 颗 4.21GHz C1-Ultra 核心、3 颗 3.5GHz C1-Premium 核心及 4 颗 2.7GHz C1-Pro 核心，单核与多核效能各增强 32% 和 17%，功耗至多降低 30%。G1-Ultta GPU 的「主机级」光追效能较上代提高了 119%，《和平精英》等游戏的高帧模式能做到全程满帧。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;天玑 9500 还支援 4 通道 UFS 4.1，并配备了高效能 + 高能效双 NPU。其中高效能 NPU 能带来 111% 效能涨幅，高能效 NPU 则负责以低功耗实现轻载 AI 模型的运算。此外新 SoC 还搭载了 Imagiq 1190 图像处理器，其追焦帧率是过去的 3 倍，2 亿画素模式可叠加额外演算法，并支援 4K60p 人像录影和 4K120p 防震。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;这款晶片还具备 1 尼特极暗显示、「蓝牙大耳朵」增强通话等特性，搭载它的手机预计于今年 Q4 大规模上市。首发产品 vivo X300 系列将于 10 月 13 日到来，同周 OPPO 也会推出相应机种。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;紧贴最新科技资讯、网购优惠，追随 Yahoo Tech 各大社交平台！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Facebook：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Instagram：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 社群：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 频道：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Telegram 频道：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://t.me/ya